@startuml
title Sequence Diagram - UC019 FinishShopping

actor "User" as Actor
boundary "ShoppingUI" as UI
control "ShoppingController" as Controller
entity "ShoppingDB" as ShoppingDB
control "PantryController" as PantryController
entity "PantryDB" as PantryDB

Actor -> UI : 1. Đánh dấu mặt hàng đã mua
activate UI
UI -> Controller : 2. markItemAsBought(itemId)
activate Controller
Controller -> ShoppingDB : 3. updateItemStatus(itemId, BOUGHT)
activate ShoppingDB
ShoppingDB --> Controller : 4. success
deactivate ShoppingDB
Controller -> PantryController : 5. transferItemToPantry(itemDetails)
activate PantryController
PantryController -> PantryDB : 6. addFood(itemDetails)
activate PantryDB
PantryDB --> PantryController : 7. success
deactivate PantryDB
PantryController --> Controller : 8. success
deactivate PantryController
Controller --> UI : 9. Thông báo chuyển vào tủ lạnh thành công
deactivate Controller
UI --> Actor : 10. Đánh dấu mặt hàng hoàn tất trên UI
deactivate UI
@enduml
